#: app/templates/admin/index.html:43
msgid "⚠️ Admin Tips"
msgstr "⚠️ Admin maslahatlari"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:45
msgid ""
"Never run in production with DEBUG enabled. Debug mode exposes internal "
"details and stack traces."
msgstr ""
"Hech qachon DEBUG yoqilgan holda ishlab chiqarishda ishlatmang. Debug rejimi"
" ichki tafsilotlar va stack izlarini ochib beradi."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:47
msgid ""
"Always deploy Grylli behind a reverse proxy (e.g. Caddy, Nginx, or Traefik) "
"and serve it over HTTPS. Sensitive user data must be encrypted in transit."
msgstr ""
"Har doim Gryllini teskari proksi (masalan, Caddy, Nginx yoki Traefik) ortiga"
" joylashtiring va HTTPS orqali xizmat qiling. Foydalanuvchilarning maxfiy "
"ma'lumotlari uzatishda shifrlangan bo'lishi kerak."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:50
msgid ""
"Ensure the data folder (database) is backed up regularly. Backups are stored"
" in the 'backups' folder."
msgstr ""
"Ma'lumotlar papkasining (bazasi) xostda zaxira nusxasi yaratilganligiga "
"ishonch hosil qiling"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:53
msgid ""
"The uploads folder is shared. To isolate attachments per user, configure "
"host-level directories and access controls."
msgstr ""
"Yuklanadigan papka umumiy. Har bir foydalanuvchi uchun biriktirmalarni "
"ajratish uchun mezbon darajasidagi kataloglar va kirish nazoratini sozlang."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:55
msgid ""
"To restore a backup: stop the container, replace the grylli.db file from a "
"backup, and restart."
msgstr ""
"Zaxira nusxasini tiklash uchun konteynerni to'xtating, data/grylli.db "
"faylini zaxira papkasidan olingan nusxasi bilan almashtiring va konteynerni "
"qayta ishga tushiring."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:56
msgid ""
"Admins cannot remove their own admin role to prevent accidental lockout."
msgstr ""
"Administatorlar o'zlarining administrator rolini o'z-o'zini qulflamasligini "
"oldini olish uchun olib tashlay olmaydilar."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:58
msgid ""
"Rate limits and automatic account lockouts are enforced to protect against "
"brute-force login attempts."
msgstr ""
"Brute-force kirish urinishlariga qarshi himoya qilish uchun stavka "
"chegaralari va avtomatik hisob qulflari amalga oshirildi."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:60
msgid ""
"Passwords, SMTP credentials, and API tokens are encrypted at rest using "
"Fernet."
msgstr ""
"Parollar, SMTP ma'lumotlari va API tokenlari Fernet yordamida turg'unlikda "
"shifrlangan."

